Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please explain to me how Makishima Shougo escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very likely that he had help from someone inside the Ministry of Welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he could have escaped otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to hear what happened directly from Makishima himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you next apprehend him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want your top priority to be bringing him in alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be putting Division 1 in charge once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth is going on? Please give me a reasonable explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginoza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you allow Enforcer Kagari to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your investigation into his disappearance\N\N has already hit a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you have been given the top\N\N priority task of recapturing Makishima,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got the perfect opportunity\N\N to sweep your blunder under the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my way of showing appreciation to Division 1 and extending my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you appreciate the consideration I'm showing you as your chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I have further orders regarding Enforcer Kougami Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to take him off this case and place him under strict supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just tell you? Your top priority is Makishima Shougo's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, the task of tracking down Kagari has been transferred to Division 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We at Division 1 are in charge of tracking down Makishima Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Enforcer Kougami, you are to remain within Bureau headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to work with Analyst Karanomori to back us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the Chief's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a bit strange that the Chief would order me off the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short on manpower as it is, and now she's reducing it further?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It suggests that the most important thing here is Makishima's safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and that stopping him from committing more crimes is merely a secondary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even say we're out to apprehend him, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,More like we've been ordered to act as his bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our top brass don't intend to judge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we manage to apprehend him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Chief intends to use him for some other purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you basing that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard what he said when he called me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He mentioned "the true form of the Sibyl System."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He had already discovered the inner workings that none of us know anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we take criminals at their word now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have negotiated with someone who can even control the Sibyl System at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, Makishima was able to outwit this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead of getting angry, they became even more obsessed with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyl is a system that is guaranteed to be independent and free from influence by any organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is given that kind of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima probably knows whether that's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They used an aircraft to transport instead of a paddy wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, only Drones were on board to guard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing about this case is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, whose body was that being taken out from the site?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been erased from the record, but we clearly saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know something's up, Ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the details are top secret. The Inspectors wouldn't know the answer, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're barking up the wrong tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go grab a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all one big farce. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Senguji Toyohisa case, I took a look at the report Gino submitted to the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I snuck a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The part where the Dominator ignored Makishima was gone without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From how the report was written,\N he was probably forced to delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The top brass are trying to erase the very fact that there are people who can't be judged by Sibyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I guess they don't have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel frustrated?{his face frustrates me}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I do. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to a realization when the riots broke out the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think enforcing justice and maintaining public order are equally important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think we can deal with those who are outside the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to make this case an exception and go back to the old system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We prosecute him, open a court, let him defend himself, and then sentence him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a pretty daunting process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it'll take to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A quicker way that won't cause anyone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've killed Makishima back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong to ask you to do it. I'll finish him off myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an Inspector, after all. I can't have his blood on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an Enforcer. I have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how our partnership works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll show my worth as a hunting dog, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not enforcing the law.{BITCH I AM THE LAW}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just replacing one killer with another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me once that you wanted to be a detective, not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do remember the most trivial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not trivial. Completely the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to those words that I didn't quit this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you always be a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me that?{foreshadowing}{SETTING UP FINAL CONFLICT}{just fuck already}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you think the Chief's throwing us a ball to play with like the dogs we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the right answer in this kind of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no right answer. All you can do is compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobuchika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to protect yourself.{CYA}{I remember when my dad gave me that talk. Except it was about sex.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said earlier, this is a game of ball between the master and their dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you disobey, you'll just be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that, you should change your position to that of a third party, neither dog nor master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A third party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to become the ball that's\N thrown about, just bouncing and rolling.{fast approaching 2deep4me territory}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At first glance, it may seem to be beneath you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but in truth, that's the way to get hurt least and avoid tiring yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the wisest course of action, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say it, but this case is too much for you to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of acting rashly and ending up being forced to resign,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're better off acting completely useless as you roll down the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some pretty terrible advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd have more smarts than me about this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the so-called wisdom that comes with age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We really can't afford not to have Kougami when we go after Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he ends up being a dog that bites his master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Makishima-related matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no other hunting dog with as keen a nose as Kougami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That detective instinct that you so often talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a talent that I don't happen to have after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Chief ordered you to take him off the case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we can get him out of the cage, the game is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only remaining question is: \Nwhat excuse shall I come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you to come up with such a radical idea, Ginoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to ask you to take part in something risky like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree that the way Kagari from your division disappeared is suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we can't let Makishima Shougo run free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have two people absent from the CID as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the present situation, we can't let you waste time sitting around in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I asked Inspector Aoyanagi in Division 2 to temporarily have you and one of her Enforcers switch places, and she agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Division 2 for a while, and help them search for Kagari Shuusei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll borrow one of the Division 2 people in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When we have so few leads on Kagari's case as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's understandable that the investigation would follow a somewhat roundabout course.{i'll be her roundabout}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami, whatever you do, don't pull any stupid stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At least not while I'm looking, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a special circumstance as defined in Code K32.{WELP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be taking Kougami Shinya into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really thought that you could outwit me with such a cheeky trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you must really take me for quite the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised to see you're such a big fan of mine, Chief Kasei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm surprised that you think you're in any position to talk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really quite hard to grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me explain! This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginoza, isn't this the sort of situation where the more you talk, the deeper you dig yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Making judgments based on your personal discretion isn't always a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is to produce a satisfying result.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, that's the sole basis for evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why it's important to know when to quit when you take a risky gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is how quickly and firmly you can close the books on your failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Inspector Ginoza...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An Enforcer under your supervision is about to commit a serious breach of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to deal with this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of just going on and on with foolish explanations,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are you able to demonstrate you can act clearly and decisively?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 265.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An Enforcer registered at the Criminal Investigation Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This target has Enforce At Will status.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}The safety will be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. An acceptable demonstration of your own worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, your lenient manner still leaves much to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enforcement mode is Non-Lethal... Para...{chute? bola? digm?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lethal... Eliminate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Ginoza. Show me how you take charge as a leader.{>doing this in front of everyone}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me that you can act decisively, unhindered by emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For a target whose Crime Coefficient is under 300,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Paralyzer mode should be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Ginoza, that Dominator appears to be faulty.{hot damn, akane}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You should send it in for maintenance immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful to Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She avoided your spine and shot you in the leg instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's gotten used to handling the Dominator, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when an inexperienced newbie rapidly becomes tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,on one hand it's reassuring, but it's also a bit sad. Complicated, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get tougher and tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that helmet still work?{oh shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less. But when the Sibyl System is completely restored, they plan on installing countermeasures.{>not patched yet}{sibyl pls}{I bet that shit was coded in Ruby}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, it'll just be a regular helmet.{Futsuu's helmetto}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How long until it's restored?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Six more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take a piece of evidence with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I need it for the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This from the guy who got taken off the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they notified you guys of that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, maybe I haven't heard yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't take it outside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking... Should I have slept with you at least once?{mfw}{confirmed for pure maiden}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I don't think we're each other's type, though.{for one thing, he's not female}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the helmet, huh? I forgot you could use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to celebrate your discharge from the hospital. Here, have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking at the info on Makishima that you collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks messy at first glance, but it's actually quite organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's prepared in such a way that you can take just the important parts, when push comes to shove.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so obsessed with Makishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it evil that you can't tolerate? Or is it Makishima himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither one, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I give up now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually I'll come to resent myself for letting Makishima Shougo get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That answer suits you perfectly, Ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from back when I worked for the Metropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I once prepared a safe house for use in emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be of use to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna leave without saying a word to the young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't face her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At least help her come to terms with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
