Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:20:02.26,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)\blur1.8}There's no way I could love anyone,
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.26,0:20:09.06,ED2top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\blur1.8}but I wish to be loved by someone in turn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:09.06,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur1.8}but I wish to be loved by someone in turn
