Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:35.01,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,300)\blur1.8\pos(815,20)}I receive no reply
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.01,0:20:46.02,ED2top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\blur1.8\pos(200,640)}I never do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:46.02,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,500)\blur1.8\pos(200,640)}I never do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. I couldn't keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to go into a line of work where I could protect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I became a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Makishima changed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man will continue to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, the law can't judge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm a detective, I can't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This case made me aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that the law can't protect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case, my only option is to step outside the law.{knew it}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsunemori Akane... There is no doubt that your way of living is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't lose sight of that just because I betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I chose a different path solely in order to have my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm aware that this is the wrong thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I know that I can only come to terms with my old self by taking the wrong path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't ask you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next time we meet, you'll be in a position to judge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When that time comes, please fulfill your duty with no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't turn your back on your beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although it was only for a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel fortunate that I was able to work under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{rest of ED}
